 $^{30}$Mg. It is concluded\nthat the cross-shell effects in the region of the island of inversion at Z=12\nare considerably more complex than previously thought and that $np - nh$\nconfigurations play a major role in the structure of $^{30}$Mg.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 27 Feb 2018 16:08:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-02-28"}
