 energy-densities of\ntensor, vector, and scalar modes at 95% credibility to $\\Omega^T_0 < 5.6 \\times\n10^{-8}$, $\\Omega^V_0 < 6.4\\times 10^{-8}$, and $\\Omega^S_0 < 1.1\\times\n10^{-7}$ at a reference frequency $f_0 = 25$ Hz.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 27 Feb 2018 22:38:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 1 Mar 2018 23:32:28 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 2 Oct 2019 16:30:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-03"}
